pageContext.claim: “Even Kristen Welker, who frankly did not a bad job considering she's totally on the other side of the plate, she looked and she said, 'Why did you say that?' You know, she's trying to save the poor guy.”
pageContext.analysis: This alleged exchange never took place in the second presidential debate. As a professional journalist moderating a debate, NBC's Kristen Welker would not be on the side of either candidate.
